    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with a strong shine, though you may find a few light stone chips on the hood and minor surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for a buyer looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that needs nothing but a new driver.",
