    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a starter vehicle for someone handy with a wrench? This car has seen plenty of adventures and definitely needs some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it offers a solid opportunity for anyone looking to put in a little work! It\u2019s priced to move and ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little elbow grease.",
