    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen remains in a state of preservation that mirrors its original showroom delivery, characterized by a flawless exterior finish and an interior devoid of discernible wear. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, its mechanical integrity is as profound as its aesthetic appeal. For the discerning individual seeking a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and condition, this offering represents a singular opportunity in the current market.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh new-car smell! It drives perfectly and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, sending power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically pristine, this chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The Laguna Seca Blue finish remains flawless with consistent paint depth across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte texture. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Full service records. Clean title. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory finish, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights its deep, mirror-like luster. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It boasts a full, documented service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. With incredibly low mileage and zero history of accidents or imperfections, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
